'''Catherine Munroe''', known in the credits as '''Cathy Munro''', is an actor who portrayed [[Zuckuss/Legends|Zuckuss]] in [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''Star Wars'': Episode V ''The Empire Strikes Back'']].<ref name="SWI 49">{{InsiderCite|49|Trail of the Bounty Hunters}}</ref> Though most notable for her appearance as the [[Gand/Legends|Gand]] [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]], Munro also had a small role as the [[Snivvian/Legends|Snivvian]] [[Wiorkettle]].<ref name="Empire at 40">{{Blogspot|subdomain=starwarsaficionado|url=2021/06/an-empire-at-40-exploring-bespin.html|name=Star Wars Aficianado|text=An Empire at 40: Exploring Bespin!}}</ref>

Munro is a close friend of actor [[Chris Parsons]], who portrayed the [[Droid/Legends|droid]] [[4-LOM/Legends|4-LOM]].<ref name="Interviews">{{WebCite|url=https://starwarsinterviews.com/original-trilogy/episode-v-the-empire-strikes-back/cathy-munroe-zuckuss|text=Cathy Munroe (Zuckuss)|author=[[Dennis Pellegrom]]|date=2010-09|work=[[Star Wars Interviews]]|archivedate=20230205201435|nolive=1}}</ref>

